Class NukkitAFKListener

java.lang.Object
com.djrapitops.plan.gathering.listeners.nukkit.NukkitAFKListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
cn.nukkit.event.Listener
public class NukkitAFKListener extends Object implements cn.nukkit.event.Listener
Listener that keeps track of actions that are not considered being AFK.

Additional Listener calls in PlayerOnlineListener to avoid having HIGHEST priority listeners.
